room_title: Escape room "Missing" by Xcape The Quandary in Tulsa
room_address: 19 East 34th St S Sand Springs, OK 74063
room_description:
You and your friends will be detectives for Sand Beach. The scenario: a concerned boyfriend reported his girlfriend missing this morning. She never showed up at the beach party Friday Night and has not returned any calls or texts from family friends.
Do you and your friends have what it takes to find out what happened in this kidnap mystery?
